{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, confirming the accuracy of a statement provided may be burdensome for the average user, which, given the lack of AI literacy of most users, will probably lead to the general acceptance of the chatbot's statement as true.",
    "All of these factors contribute to the potential risks of harm to individuals and society at large.",
    "As a consequence, regulators should be able to identify and prevent a series of risks that are linked to these factors.",
    "Building on writings from computer science and other disciplines, this paper identifies three categories of such types of risks.",
    "Firstly, policymakers and lawyers should urgently address the environmental costs of training and operating these chatbots."
  ]
}